CS Ranger
The CS Ranger is an elite Coalition scout operating deep behind enemy lines.
Better trained than the standard Grunt, Rangers combine military discipline
with wilderness survival and advanced reconnaissance skills.

CS Rangers begin with a broad military and survival skill base and choose
from Espionage, Military, Physical, Pilot, Technical, and W.P. categories.

Attribute requirements: IQ 8, PS 10, PE 10.
Starting equipment: Light Coalition scout armour, energy pistol, sniper rifle,
survival backpack, camouflage field uniform, and Coalition ID.
